cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is also a likely category as the paper deals with the k-center problem in metric spaces, which is a classic problem in computational geometry.

cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possible category as the paper deals with approximation algorithms and coreset constructions, which are topics in discrete mathematics.
